                            <comment id="12997989" author="ghelmling" created="Tue, 22 Feb 2011 19:27:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t see any reason not to do #1.  Or rather, I don&apos;t see any reason we should be using the system classloader in loadSystemCoprocessors() as opposed to the classloader used to load CoprocessorHost.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Would it work to replace the lines in CoprocessorHost.loadSystemCoprocessors():&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;      ClassLoader cl = ClassLoader.getSystemClassLoader();&lt;br/&gt;
      Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(cl);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;with &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;      ClassLoader cl = this.getClass().getClassLoader();&lt;br/&gt;
      Thread.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(cl);&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This would then use the same ClassLoader used to run the region server, right?  And should fix the problem?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Do you have a simple test case we can use?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12999690" author="apurtell" created="Sat, 26 Feb 2011 01:23:28 +0000"  >&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Would it work to replace the lines in CoprocessorHost.loadSystemCoprocessors():&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;ClassLoader&lt;/span&gt; cl = &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;ClassLoader&lt;/span&gt;.getSystemClassLoader();
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Thread&lt;/span&gt;.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(cl);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;with&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;ClassLoader&lt;/span&gt; cl = &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;.getClass().getClassLoader();
&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;Thread&lt;/span&gt;.currentThread().setContextClassLoader(cl);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;+1, seems reasonable anyway&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12999821" author="apurtell" created="Sat, 26 Feb 2011 19:18:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch removes calls to getSystemClassloader() to this.getClass().getClassLoader().&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12999824" author="stack" created="Sat, 26 Feb 2011 19:27:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;+1 Looks good to me.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
